<i>verb</i>: 허우적허우적하다 [허우저커우저카다], 허우적이다 [허우저기다], 허우적대다 [허우적때다], 허우적거리다 [허우적꺼리다], 버르적버르적하다 [버르적뻐르저카다], 버르적대다 [버르적때다], 버르적거리다 [버르적꺼리다] <br>
<ul style="list-style-type:square">
<li><i>verb</i><br>
<dt>허우적허우적하다 [허우저커우저카다]</dt><br>
<dd>1. flounder; writhe; struggle</dd><br>
<dd>손이나 발을 이리저리 자꾸 마구 흔들다.</dd><br>
<dd>To move one's arms and legs wildly, repeatedly from side to side.</dd><br>
<dd>2. flounder; struggle; strain</dd><br>
<dd>어려운 처지에서 벗어나려고 몹시 자꾸 애쓰다.</dd><br>
<dd>To make a desperate effort continuously to get out of a difficult situation.</dd><br>
<dt>허우적이다 [허우저기다]</dt><br>
<dd>1. flounder; writhe; struggle</dd><br>
<dd>손이나 발을 이리저리 마구 흔들다.</dd><br>
<dd>To move one's arms and legs wildly from side to side.</dd><br>
<dd>2. flounder; struggle; strain</dd><br>
<dd>어려운 처지에서 벗어나려고 몹시 애쓰다.</dd><br>
<dd>To make a desperate effort to get out of a difficult situation.</dd><br>
<dt>허우적대다 [허우적때다]</dt><br>
<dd>1. flounder; writhe; struggle</dd><br>
<dd>손이나 발을 자꾸 이리저리 마구 흔들다.</dd><br>
<dd>To move one's arms and legs wildly, repeatedly from side to side.</dd><br>
<dd>2. flounder; struggle; strain</dd><br>
<dd>어려운 처지에서 벗어나려고 자꾸 몹시 애쓰다.</dd><br>
<dd>To make a desperate effort continuously to get out of a difficult situation.</dd><br>
<dt>허우적거리다 [허우적꺼리다]</dt><br>
<dd>1. flounder; writhe; struggle</dd><br>
<dd>손이나 발을 자꾸 이리저리 마구 흔들다.</dd><br>
<dd>To move one's arms and legs wildly from side to side in a repeated manner.</dd><br>
<dd>2. flounder; struggle; strain</dd><br>
<dd>어려운 처지에서 벗어나려고 자꾸 몹시 애쓰다.</dd><br>
<dd>To make a desperate effort repeatedly to get out of a difficult situation.</dd><br>
<dt>버르적버르적하다 [버르적뻐르저카다]</dt><br>
<dd>struggle; flounder</dd><br>
<dd>괴롭고 힘든 상태에서 벗어나기 위해 팔다리를 마구 휘두르며 자꾸 몸을 움직이다.</dd><br>
<dd>To move one's body repeatedly while swinging one's arms and legs wildly in order to get out of a painful and difficult situation.</dd><br>
<dt>버르적대다 [버르적때다]</dt><br>
<dd>struggle; flounder</dd><br>
<dd>괴롭고 힘든 상태에서 벗어나기 위해 팔다리를 마구 휘두르며 몸을 움직이다.</dd><br>
<dd>To move one's body while swinging one's arms and legs wildly in order to get out of a painful and difficult situation.</dd><br>
<dt>버르적거리다 [버르적꺼리다]</dt><br>
<dd>struggle; flounder</dd><br>
<dd>괴롭고 힘든 상태에서 벗어나기 위해 팔다리를 마구 휘두르며 몸을 움직이다.</dd><br>
<dd>To move one's body while swinging one's arms and legs wildly in order to get out of a painful and difficult situation.</dd><br>
</li>
</ul>